{
  "id": "adv_bond_smr_01_04",
  "title": "奥山すみれ4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃじゃーん！　ここが星見プロの東京寮です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-da! This is the Hoshimi Prods. Tokyo dorm!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "へー、なんか思ってたよりもいい感じじゃん\n外観も綺麗だね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ it's actually nicer than I expected\nThe exterior looks pretty clean too~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです～！　中はもっと快適ですよ！\nさぁさぁ、どうぞ！　遠慮せず入って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right?! The inside is even more comfortable!\nCome on‚ come on! Don't be shy‚ come in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……\nすみれに流されてここまで付いて来ちゃったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…\nI let Sumire talk me into coming all the way here‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 27
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱやめとくわ\n他の奴らと顔合わせたらめんどくさそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I'll pass after all\nIt'll be a pain if I run into the others",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　まだそんなこと言うんですか！\nお家のないkanaさんを一人ぼっちには出来ません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?! You're still saying that!\nI can't leave kana-san all alone when she has nowhere to go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.7000007629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "家はあるから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a house‚ okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.4666674296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "鍵も財布もバッグごと\n全部落としちゃったんですよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you lost your keys and your wallet\nalong with your whole bag‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.4666674296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "お家の管理会社はお休みで\n今日はもう連絡取れないって言ってたじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said the management company is closed‚\nand you can't get a hold of them today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "お金がなかったらどこかにお泊まりも出来ないですし\nご飯も食べれません。お腹……空いちゃいますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have no money‚ you can't stay anywhere‚\nand you can't eat. You'll get… really hungry‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 59.066662852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "今日は寮に人も少ないですし、大丈夫です！\n私の部屋に泊まっていって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There aren't many people in the dorm today‚ so it's fine!\nPlease stay over at my place!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.066662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.066662852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "心配してくれてるのは分かるんだけど\nkanaも大人だし大丈夫だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you're worried about me\nbut I'm an adult. I'll be fine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.066662852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14500.003814700009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.5999961853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "う～、分かりました。そんなに嫌ならここでちょっと\n待ってて下さい！　貯金箱からお金持って来ます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Urgh… Okay‚ I get it. If you hate it that much‚\nplease wait here! I'll go get some money from my piggy bank!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5999961853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.9333213806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "待って！　中学生から金巻き上げるほど\nkanaの人間性終わってないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on! I'm not such a jerk\nthat I'd shake down a middle schooler for money!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9333213806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.6999880473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……泊まって行ってくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… will you stay the night?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6999880473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.1999880473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoとfranには絶対にバレたくないし）\n（{user}に助けを求めるのもなんか癪……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I definitely don't want miho and fran to find out about this）\n（And asking {user} for help feels like losing somehow…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1999880473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.0333259582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "……はあ、分かった\nじゃあ、お言葉に甘えて、今夜は泊めてもらおうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh‚ alright\nFine‚ I'll take you up on that offer and stay over tonight",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0333259582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.4666592915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "その代わり、絶対にkanaが今夜寮にいることも\n泊まったことも誰にも言わないでね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in return‚ you must never tell anyone that I was here\nor that I stayed at the dorm tonight!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4666592915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.633323415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　もちろんです！\nえへへ……kanaさんとお泊まり嬉しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Of course!\nEhehe… I'm so happy to have a sleepover with kana-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.633323415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.433323415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_04-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "（はーあ……なんかすみれといると調子狂うわ……）\n（でも、もし妹がいたらこんな感じなのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sigh… somehow‚ being around Sumire always throws me off my pace…）\n（But I wonder if this is what it feels like to have a little sister…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.433323415,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}